defaultOur 
defaultlandmark High Court victory in 2006
default 
defaultstated that 
defaultthe Israeli security forces are obliged to ensure that farmers are able to access their lands without harassment and intimidation. 
defaultIn reality, Palestinian landowners in Area C are still intimidated, harassed and prevented from accessing their lands. Radica
defaultl settlers use violence and provocation to prevent farmers from being able to reach their lands. 
defaultIt is 
defaultRHR’s presence in the field 
defaultwhich 
defaultensures that the security forces are indeed fulfilling their responsibilities to protect farmers.  
defaultR
defaultadical settlers are
default often discouraged from attacking small groups of farmers and their families
default when we are there to protect them
default. Documenting incidents of harassment and violence and using the media to publicize these events
default puts increasing pressure on the security forces t
defaulto carry out their court mandated job. 
